			<header class="comment-meta comment-author vcard">
				<img alt='' src='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/4faae231f06b4fb0c7173a1daaddbfe7?s=44&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/4faae231f06b4fb0c7173a1daaddbfe7?s=88&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' /><cite><b class="fn">David Fox</b> </cite><a href="http://activehistory.ca/papers/history-papers-12/#comment-44043"><time datetime="2013-04-29T17:52:55+00:00">April 29, 2013 at 5:52 pm</time></a>			</header><!-- .comment-meta -->

			
			<section class="comment-content comment">
				<p>Hey warbirdie, your argument is wrong and it is pathetic.</p>
<p>You never faced her choices, and you never served in Iraq like her.</p>
<p>You should read some international law as well. Iraq War is and was illegal. Get a clue.</p>
<p>&#8211; David</p>
							</section><!-- .comment-content -->

			<div class="reply">
